[[Kanada]], [[USA]], [[Gronland]] ([[Danimark]]), [[Meksik]], [[Gwatimala]], [[Salvador]], [[Honduras]], [[Custa Rika]], [[Panama]], [[Kuba]], [[Bermuda]] ([[Lingliz]]), [[Jamaika]], [[Haiti]], [[Republik n Dominik]], [[Puerto Riko]], [[Gwadilup]],[[Martinik]], [[Saint-Pierre d Mikelon]] (Fransa), Tigzirin i [[India]].

